No. (25) of 2006 on the Implementing Regulations of Law No. (23) of 2005 concerning Health Insurance

We, Mohamed Bin Zayed Al Nahyan, Crown Prince and Chairman of the Executive Council,

-Having regard to Law No. (1) of 1974 concerning the Reorganization of the Governmental Body in the Emirate of Abu Dhabi, as amended;

-LawNo. (8) of 2001 concerning the Establishment of the General Authority for Health Services for the Emirate of Abu Dhabi;

